	<h2>About me</h2>

	<p>
		I'm a senior engineer based in Bangalore, currently working on AI / ML systems at an early-stage
		B2B SaaS company. Before that, I've spent years on backend, cloud infrastructure, and the kinds
		of system design problems that don't make it into conference talks but quietly determine whether
		a startup scales or buckles.
	</p>

	<p>
		I write here partly to think more carefully about what I do day-to-day, and partly because the
		patterns I keep seeing across companies seem worth noting down.
	</p>

