	<p>
		I take on a small number of consulting engagements alongside my full-time work, focused on:
	</p>

	<ul>
		<li>Backend architecture reviews for early-stage SaaS</li>
		<li>Cloud cost optimization (AWS / GCP)</li>
		<li>API design, data pipelines, and database scaling</li>
		<li>Migration planning (monolith → services, on-prem → cloud)</li>
	</ul>

	<p>
		If you're building something in this space and want a senior pair of eyes for a few hours
